ew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20quotes%20from%20unnamed%20Western%20allied%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20Vancouver%20in%20Canada%20on%20June%2018.%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20allegation%20that%20India%20is%20behind%20the%20murder%20has%20led%20to%20a%20diplomatic%20crisis%20between%20the%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20report%20comes%20after%20United%20States%20Ambassador%20to%20Canada%2C%20David%20Cohen%2C%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctvnews.ca%2Fpolitics%2Fshared-intelligence-from-five-eyes-informed-trudeau-s-india-allegation-u-s-ambassador-1.6574265%5C%22%3ECTV%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Canadian%20news%20channel%2C%20that%20it%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cshared%20intelligence%20among%20Five%20Eye%20partners%E2%80%9D%20that%20prompted%20Trudeau%20to%20go%20public%20with%20his%20explosive%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20quotes%20officials%20who%20said%20that%20while%20US%20intelligence%20agencies%20offered%20their%20Canadian%20counterparts%20%E2%80%9Ccontext%20that%20helped%20Canada%20conclude%20that%20India%20had%20been%20involved%E2%80%A6what%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20%E2%80%9Csmoking%20gun%2C%E2%80%9D%20intercepted%20communications%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%20in%20Canada%20indicating%20involvement%20in%20the%20plot%2C%20was%20gathered%20by%20Canadian%20officials.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20told%20%3Cem%3ENYT%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20US%20did%20not%20learn%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20plot%20until%20after%20Nijjar%20was%20killed.%20Nor%20did%20they%20know%20of%20the%20plot%20to%20kill%20him.%20They%20also%20said%20that%20had%20they%20known%20of%20the%20risk%2C%20they%20would%20have%20immediately%20informed%20Ottawa.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20officials%2C%20notably%2C%20had%20warned%20Nijjar%20of%20the%20risk%20to%20his%20life.%3C%