er%20is%20getting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20the%20right%20decision%20because%20it's%20very%20important%20for%20a%20player%20to%20understand%20himself%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportskeeda.com%2Fcricket%2Fnews-sanju-samson-listen-someone-asks-play-according-pitch-sreesanth-wicketkeeper-batter-s-snub-2023-world-cup-squad%5C%22%3ESportskeeda%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20Gavaskar%20sir%20to%20Harsha%20Bhogle%20sir%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravi%20Shastri%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41719-ravishankar-jayadritha-shastri-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavi%20Shastri%3C%2Fa%3E%20sir%2C%20everyone%20rates%20him%20highly.%20There's%20no%20doubt%20about%20his%20ability.%20But%20the%20approach...%20he%20doesn't%20listen%20when%20someone%20asks%20him%20to%20play%20according%20to%20pitch.%20He%20can%20change%20that%20attitude.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESreesanth%20said%20that%20he%20even%20had%20a%20chat%20with%20Samson%20over%20his%20application%20on%20the%2022-yard%20strip.%20But%2C%20the%20former%20pacer%20remains%20disappointed%20to%20see%20the%20wicket-keeper%20batter%20failing%20to%20show%20the%20sort%20of%20consistency%20that%20a%20player%20at%20his%20level%20should.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhenever%20I%20meet%20him%2C%20I%20tell%20him%20just%20one%20thing%3A%20%26quot%3BSanju%2C%20please%20read%20the%20wicket.%20Wait%2C%20don't%20go%20after%20every%20bowler.%20Think.%20You%20can%20hit%20anyone%20anywhere%20anytime%2C%20just%20wait%20for%20the%20opportunity%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESamson%20has%20a%20huge%20fan%20following%2C%20and%20Sreesanth%20isn't%20unaware%20of%20that.%20The%202011%20World%20Cup-winning%20India%20speedster%20feels%20Samson%20is%20getting%20plenty%20of%20Sympathy%20from%20his%20fans%2C%20but%20not%20the%20sort%20of%20appreciation%20for%20his%20performances%20that%20is%20required%20to%20excel%20at%20this%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20Malyali%20people%20who%20support%20him%2C%20including%20me%2C%20say%20he%20doesn't%20get%20chances.%20We%20can't%20say%20that.%20He%20got%20chances%20against%20Ireland%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20he%20has%20been%20playing%20IPL%20for%2010%20years.%20He%20has%20been%20playing%20since%202013%2C%20has%20been%20the%20captain%20too%2C%20and%20has%20scored%20just%20three%20100s%20and%20he%20hasn't%20shown%20consistency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20say%2C%20'Waqt%20kiske%20liye%20nahi%20rukta'%20(time%20doesn't%20stop%20for%20anyone).%20Everyone%20talks%20about%20time%2C%20I'll%20also%20tell%20the%20same%20to%20Sanju.%20A%20lot%20of%20good%20people%20are%20coming%20in.%20Even%20the%20two%20keepers%20going%20for%20the%20Asia%20Games%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Prabhsimran%20Singh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110976-simran-singh-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPrabhsimran%20Singh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jitesh%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F106754-jitesh-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJitesh%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E).%20When%20everyone's%20talking%20about%20you%2C%20make%20it%20count.%20Getting%20sympathy%20is%20very%20easy%2C%20but%20appreciation%20is%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESreesanth%2C%20however%2C%20remains%20confident%20that%20Samson%20will%20be%20back%20in%20the%20Indian%20team.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20feels%20the%20Kerala%20batter%20could%20succeed%20in%20all%20three%20formats%20of%20the%20game%20if%20he%20alters%20his%20mindset%20a%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20will%20be%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20Sreesanth%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe'll%20play%20all%20formats%3A%20Tests%2C%20ODIs%20and%20T20s%20if%20he%20changes%20his%20mindset.%20I%20don't%20think%20he'll%20change%20his%20mindset%20but%20I%20genuinely%20hope%20for%20Kerala%20cricket%20and%20Indian%20cricket%20that%20such%20a%20talent%20doesn't%20get%20wasted%20by%20only%20playing%20the%20IPL.%20I%20think%20he%20should%20change%20his%20approach%20but%20he%20will%20not...%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20change%20a%20person%20who%20doesn't%20want%20to%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695534120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F7pgrufi8_sanju-samson_625x300_02_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgetting-sympathy-is-easy-but-s-sreesanth-rips-into-sanju-samson-4418565%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22S%20Sreesanth%20isn't%20in%20agreement%20with%20the%20public%20sentiment%20with%20regards%20to%20Sanju%20Samson's%20absence%20from%20India's%20ODI%20team.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgetting-sympathy-is-easy-but-s-sreesanth-rips-into-sanju-samson-4418565%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgetting-sympathy-is-easy-but-s-sreesanth-rips-into-sanju-samson-4418565%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgetting-sympathy-is-easy-but-s-sreesanth-rips-into-sanju-samson-4418565%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deadline%20to%20add%20nominees%20for%20MF%20investors%2C%20demat%20account%20ends%20on%20Sep%2030%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695533961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2020-07%2F10%2Ffull%2F1594386256-7532.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fmutual-fund%2Fdeadline-to-add-nominees-for-mf-investors-demat-account-ends-on-sep-30-123092400177_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20mandate%20applies%20to%20both%20new%20as%20well%20as%20existing%20investors%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(Sebi)%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en