20it.%20But%20there's%20also%20political%20resistance%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20are%20occupying%20positions%20of%20influence%2C%20we%20see%20this%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20most%20of%20all%2C%20are%20resisting%20the%20pressure%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20are%20economically%20dominant%20today%20are%20leveraging%20their%20production%20capabilities%20and%20those%20who%20have%20institutional%20influence%20or%20historical%20influence%20have%20actually%20weaponised%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20capabilities%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20will%20all%20mouth%20the%20right%20things%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20is%20still%20today%2C%20it's%20a%20world%20very%20much%20of%20double%20standards%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECOVID%20itself%20was%20an%20example%20of%20it%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20think%20this%20whole%20transition%20will%20really%20be%20in%20a%20sense%20the%20global%20South%20putting%20more%20and%20more%20pressure%20on%20the%20international%20system.%20And%2C%20the%20global%20North%E2%80%A6it's%20not%20just%20the%20North.%20There%20are%20parts%20which%20may%20not%20think%20of%20themselves%20in%20the%20North%2C%20but%20are%20very%20resistant%20to%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20added%20cultural%20rebalancing%20really%20means%20recognising%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20world%2C%20respecting%20the%20diversity%20of%20the%20world%2C%20and%20giving%20other%20cultures%20and%20other%20traditions%20their%20due%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20referred%20to%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20Delhi%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20cited%20the%20example%20of%20millets.%20He%20noted%20that%20the%20global%20South%20historically%20ate%20less%20wheat%20and%20more%20millets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20name%20of%20the%20market%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20are%20done%2C%20like%20in%20the%20name%20of%20freedom%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20are%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20laughter%20from%20the%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERespecting%20others'%20heritage%2C%20tradition%2C%20music%2C%20literature%2C%20and%20ways%20of%20life%2C%20this%20is%20all%20part%20of%20the%20change%20that%20the%20global%20South%20would%20like%20to%20see%2C%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20also%20addressed%20by%20India's%20Permanent%20Representative%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Ambassador%20Ruchira%20Kamboj%2C%20Reliance%20Foundation%20CEO%20Jagannatha%20Kumar%2C%20UN%20Resident%20Coordinator%20in%20India%20Shombi%20Sharp%20and%20ORF%20President%20Samir%20Saran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParticipating%20in%20the%20panel%20discussion%20at%20the%20event%20were%20the%20Minister%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20of%20Portugal%20Joao%20Gomes%20Cravinho%20and%20the%20Minister%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20and%20Foreign%20Trade%2C%20Jamaica%2C%20Kamina%20Johnson%20Smith.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20further%20said%20that%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20of%20India's%20G20%20Presidency%20still%20left%20before%20Brazil%20assumes%20the%20presidency%20in%20December%202023%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20will%20get%20hopefully%20something%20moving%20on%20the%20reform%20of%20international%20financial%20institutions.%E2%80%9D%20Saran%20referred%20to%20Jaishankar's%20remark%20that%20%26quot%3BEurope's%20problems%20are%20the%20world's%20problems%20but%20the%20world's%20problems%20are%20not%20Europe's%20problems%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20some%20feel%20that%20Jaishankar%20is%20tough%20on%20Europe%20and%20if%20that%20is%20a%20fair%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20no%20of%20course%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20added%20that%20among%20the%20main%20issues%20that%20are%20troubling%20the%20entire%20world%20are%20debt%2C%20SDG%20(Sustainable%20Development%20Goal)%20resourcing%2C%20climate%20action%20resourcing%2C%20digital%20access%2C%20nutrition%20and%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20said%20that%20partly%20because%20of%20COVID%20and%20partly%20due%20to%20the%20focus%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthese%20subjects%20were%20driven%20out%20of%20the%20global%20conversations%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cto%20get%20actually%20the%20G20%20to%20talk%20about%20what%20the%20world%20wanted%20it%20to%20talk%20about%20-%20that%20was%20a%20real%20problem%20in%20the%20G20.%E2%80%9D%20He%20asserted%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20put%20it%20very%20well%20when%20he%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20let's%20talk%20to%20the%20people%20who%20are%20not%20going%20to%20be%20on%20the%20table%2C%20let's%20find%20out%20what%20they%20have%20to%20say%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20is%20why%20India%20did%20the%20Voice%20of%20Global%20South%20Summit%E2%80%932023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHosting%20the%20Voice%20of%20Global%20South%20Summit%20gave%20India%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20credentials%2C%20actually%20the%20empirical%20basis%20really%20to%20say%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe've%20spoken%20to%20125%20countries%20and%20this%20is%20really%20what%20is%20troubling%20them%20and%20that%20is%20why%20we%20need%20to%20focus%20on%20these%20issues.%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20YAS%20NSA%20NSA%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695533460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F2jejnmdo_jaishankar-pti_625x300_08_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstill-a-world-of-double-standards-s-jaishankars-swipe-at-dominant-nations-4418513%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20said%20that%20it%20is%20still%20a%20world%20of%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20standards%26quot%3B%20and%20those%20countries%20which%20are%20occupying%20positions%20of%20influence%20are%20resisting%20the%20pressure