ession.%20He%20did%20not%20elaborate%20what%20the%20eight%20bills%20were.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament%20is%20going%20to%20start%20for%20five%20days%20from%20tomorrow%2C%20for%20which%20a%20total%20of%208%20bills%20are%20listed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20first%20day%2C%20the%20session%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20old%20Parliament%20House.%20The%20next%20day%20i.e.%20on%2019th%20September%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20photo%20session%20in%20the%20old%20Parliament%20House%2C%20then%20there%20will%20be%20a%20function%20in%20the%20Central%20Hall%20at%2011%20am.%20After%20that%20we%20will%20enter%20the%20new%20Parliament.%20The%20Parliament%20session%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20new%20Parliament%20House%20on%20September%2019%20and%20regular%20parliamentary%20work%20will%20begin%20from%20September%2020%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20learnt%20that%20opposition%20parties%2C%20during%20the%20all-party%20meeting%20on%20September%2017%2C%20also%20raised%20objections%20to%20the%20Election%20Commissioners%E2%80%99%20Bill%20which%20has%20drawn%20criticism%20over%20its%20implications%20for%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commissioners-appointment-bill-farewell-to-free-and-fair-elections%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20free%20and%20fair%20elections%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20country%20and%20the%20proposed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fumpire-cannot-be-subordinate-to-team-captain%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edowngrading%20of%20the%20status%20of%20Election%20Commissioners.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20evening%20of%20September%2018%2C%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20was%20held%20in%20which%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20bill%20was%20approved.%20However%2C%20after%20the%20meeting%20there%20was%20no%20usual%20cabinet%20briefing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20Union%20minister%2C%20Prahlad%20Singh%20Patel%2C%20who%20had%20tweeted%20about%20the%20approval%20given%20to%20the%20Bill%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomens-reservation-bill-cabinet-clear-33-percent%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edeleted%20his%20post%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Ehours%20later.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20only%20in%20his%20speech%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20the%20next%20day%2C%20September%2020%2C%20that%20Modi%20confirmed%20that%20the%20cabinet%20had%20approved%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20the%20night%20before%20while%20announcing%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPerhaps%20I%20have%20been%20chosen%20by%20god%20to%20do%20this%20auspicious%20work.%20Once%20again%20our%20government%20has%20taken%20a%20step%20in%20this%20direction.%20In%20yesterday%E2%80%99s%20cabinet%20meeting%2C%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20was%20approved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequently%2C%20Union%20minister%20for%20law%20and%20justice%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20tabled%20the%20Bill%2C%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20passed%20the%20legislation%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20next%20two%20days.%20While%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-passes-womens-reservation-bill-amit-shah-implementation-2029%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etwo%20MPs%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20opposed%20the%20bill%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20it%20was%20passed%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fno-date-set-for-implementation-as-womens-reservation-bill-is-passed-unanimously-by-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eunanimously%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20though%20no%20date%20has%20been%20set%20for%20its%20implementation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%2C%20the%20special%20session%20also%20saw%20a%20discussion%20on%2075%20years%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20journey%20on%20September%2018%2C%20and%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20achievements%20of%20Chandrayaan%203%20on%20September%2020%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20on%20September%2021%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20special%20session%20then%20ended%20a%20day%20early%20on%20Thursday%20(September%2021).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20bill%2C%20it%20did%20not%20take%20up%20any%20of%20the%20other%20legislative%20business%20listed%20in%20the%20tentative%20house%20agenda%2C%20nor%20was%20there%20a%20new%20list%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Ceight%20bills%E2%80%9D%20that%20Joshi%20referred%20to%20after%20the%20all-party%20meeting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFarm%20bills%2C%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20and%20so%20on%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Rules%20of%20Procedure%20and%20Conduct%20of%20Business%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20transaction%20of%20government%20business%20is%20organised%20by%20the%20secretary%20general%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Speaker%20on%20consultation%20with%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20House.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CProvided%20that%20such%20order%20of%20business%20shall%20not%20be%20varied%20on%20the%20day%20that%20business%20is%20set%20down%20for%20disposal%20unless%20the%20Speaker%20is%20satisfied%20that%20there%20is%20sufficient%20ground%20for%20such%20variation%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20P.D.T.%20Achary%2C%20an%20expert%20in%20parliamentary%20affairs%20and%20former%20Secretary%20General%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20while%20the%20rules%20of%20parliamentary%20procedure%20allow%20the%20government%20to%20change%20the%20items%20of%20legislative%20business%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20it%20cannot%20%E2%80%9Cbecome%20regular%20practice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20might%20have%20happened%20before%20(that%20bills%20are%20listed%20at%20the%20last%20minute)%2C%20but%20this%20was%20not%20as%20frequent%20as%20it%20is%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTake%20the%20case%20of%20the%20three%20farm%20bills%20or%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%20All%20these%20bills%20were%20introduced%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20without%20the%20house%20knowing%20about%20it.%20No%20member%20had%20any%20notice.%20These%20rules%20have%20been%20framed%20keeping%20in%20view%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20members%2C%20who%20have%20to%20be%20given%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20bill%2024%20hours%20before%20so%20they%20can%20come%20prepared%20and%20raise%20objections%20to%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20bill%2C%20if%20they%20wish%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20expert%20said%20that%20while%20there%20can%20be%20situations%20where%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20urgently%20legislate%20on%20a%20certain%20issue%20and%20changes%20the%20order%20of%20business%20and%20the%20Speaker%20can%20allow%20the%20government%20to%20do%20so%20using%20his%20discretionary%20powers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20this%20has%20become%20a%20practice%20and%20this%20shows%20a%20pattern%20now.%20It%20shows%20that%20many%20of%20these%20important%20bills%20were%20introduced%20without%20giving%20sufficient%20notice%20to%20the%20members%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20good%20practice%20and%20against%20the%20rules.%20Yes%2C%20the%20Speaker%20has%20the%20discretion%20but%20he%20has%20to%20use%20his%20judgement%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20issue.%20This%20discretion%20is%20not%20to%20be%20used%20regularly.%20That%20means%20the%20rules%20become%20obsolete%20then.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20bill%20is%20being%20brought%20in%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20and%20that%20has%20become%20a%20practice%20it%20shows%20that%20the%20government%20has%20no%20plans%20about%20its%20legislative%20business%20in%20advance%2C%20which%20has%20to%20be%20planned%20and%20accordingly%20the%20house%20has%20to%20be%20notified.%20And%20that%20happens%20every%20time.%20You%20cannot%20depart%20from%20it%20whenever%20you%20like%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20parliamentary%20affairs%20expert%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Secrecy%20hurts%20democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20MP%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20the%20special%20session%20agenda%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Csmokescreen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20said%20before%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20as%20well%2C%20that%20the%20special%20session%20will%20be%20a%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Echalisaa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ramesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20Chandrayaan%2C%20then%20people%20came%20prepared%20for%20other%20bills%20that%20were%20not%20taken%20up.%20It%20started%20with%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20western%20calendar%20birthday%20and%20ended%20with%20his%20Hindu%20calendar%20birthday.%20If%20they%20wanted%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20it%20would%20have%20been%20passed%20in%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20itself.%20It%20was%20a%20smokescreen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20debate%20on%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%2C%20All%20India%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20secrecy%20of%20the%20house%20agenda%20while%20voicing%20his%20support%20for%20the%20legislation%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20will%20this%20government%20learn%20that%20we%20are%20a%20parliamentary%20democracy%2C%20not%20an%20army%20commando%20top%20secret%20operation.%20In%20an%20army%20commando%20operation%2C%20you%20need%20secrecy%2C%20you%20need%20surprise%2C%20you%20need%20stealth.%20In%20a%20parliamentary%20democracy%20you%20don%E2%80%99t.%20You%20need%20cooperation%2C%20you%20need%20sharing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20you%20need%20this%20special%20session%2C%20no%20agenda%2C%20the%20agenda%20will%20be%20added%20later.%20Why%20do%20you%20have%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20on%20Sunday%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20mention%20a%20word%20about%20this%20bill%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20have%20a%20cabinet%20meeting%20and%20this%20morning%20we%20are%20given%20four%20hours%20to%20give%20amendments.%20I%20appeal%20to%20them%2C%20parliamentary%20democracy%20with%20such%20secrecy%20hurts%20a%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20who%20was%20suspended%20during%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%2C%20said%20that%20it%20appears%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20no%20preparations%20for%20the%20special%20session.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20had%20no%20preparations.%20If%20they%20had%20to%20pass%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservations%20Bill%20and%20it%20was%20not%20going%20to%20come%20into%20force%20in%202024%2C%20then%20why%20did%20they%20not%20get%20it%20passed%20in%20the%20Winter%20Session%3F%20They%20sang%20praises%20about%20Chandrayaan%20during%20the%20session.%20What%20use%20did%20they%20make%20of%20the%20special%20session%3F%20The%20women%E2%80%99s%20reservation%20Bill%20will%20not%20come%20in%202024%20so%20there%20was%20no%20emergency%20for%20that%20either.%20The%20Election%20Commissioner%E2%80%99s%20Bill%20was%20opposed%20to%20in%20the%20all%20party%20meeting%20so%20they%20stepped%20back%20from%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReferring%20to%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Faap-announces-nationwide-protest-against-sanjay-singhs-rajya-sabha-suspension-manipur-turmoil%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuspension%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20raising%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20action%20against%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Framesh-bidhuri-danish-ali-lok-sabha-hate-speech%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EBJP%20MP%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20who%20used%20communal%20slurs%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%2C%20Singh%20said%20that%20parliamentary%20processes%20are%20being%20made%20into%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmockery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20in%20which%20parliamentary%20processes%20are%20being%20reduced%20to%20a%20joke%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20parliament%20itself%20will%20lose%20its%20meaning.%C2%A0%20Outside%20the%20parliament%2C%20they%20are%20using%20central%20agencies%20like%20ED%2C%20CBI%20to%20threaten%20opposition%20parties%20and%20topple%20governments%20run%20by%20opposition%20parties.%20Parliament%20was%20the%20only%20platform%20to%20raise%20your%20issues%20but%20now%20the%20extension%20of%20my%20suspension%20by%20the%20parliamentary%20privilege%20committee%20and%20the%20lack%20of%20action%20against%20Bidhuri%20just%20shows%20what%20is%20happening%20to%20the%20parliamentary%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Kakoli%20Ghosh%20Dastidar%20said%20that%20while%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20Bill%20was%20important%2C%20and%20a%20longstanding%20demand%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20appears%20to%20have%20camouflaged%20its%20electoral%20agenda%20in%20the%20special%20session.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20government%20is%20more%20interested%20in%20their%20electoral%20gains%20than%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20welfare.%20The%20hidden%20agenda%20being%20the%20election%20was%20camouflaged%20(in%20the%20special%20session).%20They%20are%20not%20interested%20in%20welfare%20and%20only%20in%20electoral%20gimmicks%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20women%E2%80%99s%20bill%20is%20a%20very%20important%20bill%20but%20it%20was%20our%20wish%20that%20it%20be%20implemented%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20It%20has%20been%20used%20to%20fool%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20clause%20tied%20to%20the%20legislation%20that%20it%20will%20only%20be%20implemented%20after%20the%20census%20and%20delimitation%20exercises%20are%20done.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20the%20utility%20of%20the%20special%20session.%20We%20just%20finished%20the%20monsoon%20session%20and%20another%20is%20coming%20in%20winter.%20Chandrayaan%20is%20the%20scientists%E2%80%99%20accomplishment%2C%20not%20the%20government%E2%80%99s.%20This%20is%20just%20to%20propagate%20themselves%20and%20call%20a%20special%20session%20and%20spend%20crores%20of%20money%20and%20pick%20up%20two%20issues%20which%20are%20actually%20of%20the%20scientists%20and%20the%20opposition%20parties%20when%20they%20were%20in%20power%20and%20to%20shift%20to%20a%20new%20building%20on%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi.%20My%20religion%20is%20my%20own%20but%20it%20cannot%20be%20used%20to%20dominate%20other%20people%20and%20use%20it%20for%20votes..So%20in%20every%20way%20their%20target%20is%20elections%20which%20are%20coming%20up%20in%20five%20states%20this%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20national%20spokesperson%20Syed%20Zafar%20Islam%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20there%20was%20no%20secrecy%C2%A0%20behind%20the%20special%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20has%20the%20discretion%20and%20the%20flexibility%20to%20change%20bills%20or%20introduce%20a%20different%20bill%20if%20it%20wants.%20Everybody%20was%20informed%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20special%20session%20and%20enough%20time%20was%20given%20to%20everyone%20to%20prepare.%20See%20the%20outcome%2C%20everyone%20supported%20the%20Bill.%20If%20they%20had%20not%20read%20it%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20supported%20it.%20They%20have%20vehemently%20opposed%20other%20bills.%20But%20this%20bill%20everyone%20supported%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695532651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24104222%2FF6Y_Ed2bsAAxZsm.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fparliament-procedure-secrecy-special-session%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lone%20legislative%20business%20that%20was%20conducted%20during%20the%20special%20session%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20tentative%20agenda%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20released%20on%20September%2013.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fparliament-procedure-secrecy-special-session%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kiku%20Sharda%20mourns%20the%20demise%20of%20his%20parents%2C%20writes%20Lost%20them%20both%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695531653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103901612%2Cimgsize-1353517.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fkiku-sharda-mourns-the-demise-of-his-parent