this-giant-donut-wins-guinness-world-record-title-guess-its-weight-4400057%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E).%20Before%20that%2C%20it%20was%20the%20record%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.com%2Fnews%2Fmexican-candy-company-creates-world-record-for-largest-marshmallow-that-weighs-648-kg-4206667%5C%22%3Eworld's%20largest%20marshmallow%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20took%20the%20Internet%20by%20storm.%20But%20it's%20not%20just%20culinary%20creations%20that%20go%20down%20in%20history.%20People%20with%20unusual%20food-related%20skills%20are%20also%20often%20recognised%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.com%2Fnews%2Fcan-you-make-a-sandwich-in-40-seconds-this-german-duo-did-and-they-have-a-world-record-4058417%5C%22%3EGuinness%20World%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E%20(GWR).%20Among%20the%20recent%20achievements%20is%20that%20of%20an%20Indian%20man%20drinking%20a%20particular%20type%20of%20juice%20at%20a%20record-breaking%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.com%2Fnews%2Ficymi-6-recent-food-related-world-records-that-will-surprise-you-4362044%5C%22%3EICYMI%3A%206%20Recent%20Food-Related%20World%20Records%20That%20Will%20Surprise%20You%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFayis%20Nazer%20performed%20the%20extraordinary%20feat%20of%20drinking%20a%20Capri%20Sun%20within%20a%20span%20of%208.02%20seconds.%20Nazer%20has%20become%20the%20only%20person%20to%20have%20achieved%20the%20task%20within%2010%20seconds.%20Interestingly%2C%20Nazer%20had%20once%20held%20the%20same%20record%20with%20a%20time%20span%20of%2011.86%20seconds.%20But%20he%20was%20dethroned%20by%20a%20German%20man%20named%20Andre%20Ortolf%20last%20year%20when%20he%20managed%20to%20perform%20the%20same%20action%20in%2010.41%20seconds.%20With%20his%20latest%20feat%20of%208.02%20seconds%2C%20Nazer%20has%20reclaimed%20the%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.