lligence%20among%20Five%20Eyes%20partners%26quot%3B%20that%20informed%20Trudeau's%20public%20allegation%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20link%20between%20the%20government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20CTV%20News%20Channel%2C%20Canada's%2024-hour%20all-news%20network%2C%20reported%20quoting%20the%20US%20Ambassador%20to%20Canada%20David%20Cohen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E'Five%20Eyes'%20network%20is%20an%20intelligence%20alliance%20consisting%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20Australia%2C%20Canada%20and%20New%20Zealand.%20It%20is%20both%20surveillance-based%20and%20signals%20intelligence%20(SIGINT).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustin%20Trudeau%20had%20on%20September%2018%20made%20an%20explosive%20allegation%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bpotential%26quot%3B%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20agents%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20extremist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20citizen%2C%20in%20Surrey%20in%20British%20Columbia%20on%20June%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20rejected%20Trudeau's%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Babsurd%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmotivated.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Canadian%20diplomat%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20move%20to%20Ottawa's%20expulsion%20of%20an%20Indian%20official%20over%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20India%20designated%20Nijjar%2C%2045%2C%20as%20a%20terrorist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CTV's%20report%20is%20based%20on%20its%20exclusive%20interview%20on%20CTV's%20programme%20'Question%20Period%20with%20Vassy%20Kapelos'%20that%20is%20to%20air%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECTV%20quoted%20Cohen%20as%20saying%20that%20he%20confirmed%3A%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20shared%20intelligence%20among%20Five%20Eyes%20partners%20that%20helped%20lead%20Canada%20to%20make%20the%20statements%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20made.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20days%20since%2C%20as%20diplomatic%20tensions%20continue%20to%20ratchet%20up%20-%20from%20Canada%20reassessing%20its%20staffing%20in%20India%2C%20to%20India%20suspending%20visa%20services%20for%20Canadians%20-%20there%20have%20been%20swirling%20questions%20about%20what%20intelligence%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20this%20story%2C%20who%20was%20aware%20of%20it%2C%20and%20when%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CTV%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20added%20that%20while%20Cohen%20would%20not%20comment%20on%20whether%20the%20intelligence%20informing%20the%20Canadian%20government's%20investigation%20was%20both%20human%20and%20surveillance-based%2C%20or%20whether%20it%20included%20signals%20intelligence%20of%20Indian%20diplomats%2C%20the%20US%20envoy%20to%20Canada%20did%20say%20%26quot%3Bthere%20was%20shared%20intelligence%20among%20Five%20Eyes%20partners%20that%20helped%20lead%20Canada%20to%20making%20the%20statements%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20made.%26quot%3B%20This%20is%20the%20first%20admission%20by%20any%20US%20government%20official%20about%20the%20sharing%20of%20intelligence%20by%20Five%20Eyes%20partners%20with%20Canada%20even%20when%20there%20were%20multiple%20unofficial%20and%20non-official%20reports%20about%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CTV%20report%20also%20mentioned%20that%20there%20were%20reports%20from%20the%20Canadian%20Broadcasting%20Corporation%20(CBC)%20and%20The%20Associated%20Press%20that%20the%20intelligence%20Trudeau%20was%20speaking%20of%20did%20not%20come%20from%20Canada%20alone%20and%20that%20additional%20information%20was%20provided%20by%20an%20unspecified%20member%20of%20the%20intelligence-sharing%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Cohen)%20made%20this%20comment%20while%20denying%20a%20Washington%20Post%20report%20alleging%20that%20weeks%20before%20Trudeau's%20bombshell%20declaration%2C%20Ottawa%20asked%20its%20closest%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20US%20to%20publicly%20condemn%20the%20murder%20and%20that%20overture%20was%20rebuffed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CTV%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVer