%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103898886%2Cimgsize-218434.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fbjp-jds-alliance-a-marriage-of-convenience-or-emerging-double-engine%2Farticleshow%2F103898863.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20(JD(S))%20have%20formed%20an%20alliance%20in%20Karnataka%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Despite%20ideological%20differences%2C%20the%20two%20parties%20have%20joined%20forces%20to%20counter%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20BJP%20aims%20to%20make%20inroads%20in%20the%20Vokkaliga%20stronghold%2C%20where%20it%20has%20historically%20performed%20poorly.%20The%20alliance%20also%20seeks%20to%20consolidate%20support%20from%20the%20Lingayat%20and%20Vokkaliga%20communities.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20concerns%20that%20this%20alliance%20may%20hurt%20the%20BJP%20more%20than%20the%20JD(S)%20in%20a%20three-way%20contest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22MANUAIYAPPA%20KANATHANDA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20To%20Flag%20Off%209%20New%20Vande%20Bharat%20Trains%20Today.%20Check%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20flag%20off%20nine%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20trains%20today%20that%20will%20help%20improve%20connectivity%20across%2011%20states.%20The%20new%20trains%20will%20be%20the%20fastest%20on%20the%20routes%20and%20will%20bring%20down%20travel%20time%20for%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Udaipur%20%E2%80%93%20Jaipur%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20train%20will%20boost%20connectivity%20between%20Udaipur%20and%20Jaipur.%20It%20will%20be%20about%2030%20minutes%20faster%20than%20the%20fastest%20train%20that%20currently%