C2%A0CM%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%2C%20was%20made%C2%A0Haryana%C2%A0Congress%C2%A0chief%20in%202022.%20He%20replaced%20Kumari%20Selja%20who%20was%20made%20AICC%20in-charge%20of%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20remarks%2C%20Bhan%20remained%20unapologetic%20claiming%20that%20his%20words%20%E2%80%9Cwere%20Haryanvi%20slang%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20have%20I%20said%20that%20is%20wrong%E2%80%A6I%20have%20only%20described%20the%20truth.%20Is%20this%20language%20wrong%2C%20this%20is%20a%20normal%20language%20in%20Haryana.%20We%20call%20unmarried%20men%20by%20this%20slang%20in%20Haryana%20and%20that%20is%20not%20an%20abuse%2C%26quot%3B%20Udai%20Bhan%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20only%20spoken%20the%20truth.%20If%20I%20had%20said%20something%20wrong%2C%20like%20what%20was%20said%20by%20that%20MP%2C%20I%20would%20have%20apologised.%20This%20is%20just%20a%20light%20comment%20made%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20which%20has%20been%20made%20into%20a%20needless%20issue.%20This%20is%20normal%20language%20used%20in%C2%A0Haryana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0BJP%C2%A0has%20demanded%20that%20the%C2%A0Congress%C2%A0take%20action%20against%20its%20state%20unit%20chief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EParty%20Spokesperson%20and%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20alleged%20that%C2%A0Congress%C2%A0has%20always%20used%20this%20kind%20of%20language%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20video%20has%20caused%20extreme%20pain%20and%20anguish%20among%C2%A0BJP%C2%A0workers%20and%20the%20common%20man.%20This%20is%20below-the-belt%20language%2C%20it%20is%20the%20height%20of%20low-level%20politics%20which%20is%20being%20played%20by%20the%C2%A0Congress.%C2%A0Congress%C2%A0has%20always%20used%20this%20kind%20of%20language%20for%20the%20PM%20and%20his%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20one%20of%20our%20MPs%20made%20an%20unparliamentary%20remark%20