emic%20extended%20a%20helping%20hand%20by%20providing%20made-in-India%20vaccines%20to%20nearly%20100%20countries%20and%20supplying%20medicines%20to%20150%20nations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMany%20of%20you%20would%20recall%20that%20throughout%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20India%20had%20extended%20a%20helping%20hand%20by%20providing%20made-in-India%20vaccines%20to%20nearly%20100%20countries%20and%20supplying%20medicines%20to%20150%20nations%2C%20earning%20us%20the%20moniker%20'The%20Pharmacy%20of%20the%20World%2C'%26quot%3B%20Ruchira%20Kamboj%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Kamboj%20said%20that%20India's%20development%20partnerships%20have%20expanded%20significantly.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20India-UN%20Development%20Partnership%20Fund%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20has%20successfully%20developed%20a%20portfolio%20of%2075%20projects%20across%2056%20developing%20nations%20in%20six%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeantime%2C%20our%20development%20partnerships%20have%20also%20expanded%20significantly%2C%20reaching%2078%20nations%20across%20diverse%20regions%20and%20we%20have%2C%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20initiated%20600%20projects%20that%20stand%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20goodwill%20for%20our%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Kamboj%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCapacity%20building%20is%20also%20at%20the%20core%20of%20our%20development%20philosophy%2C%20and%20we%20have%20offered%20training%20to%20200%2C000%20individuals%20from%20over%20160%20countries%2C%20prioritizing%20the%20needs%20of%20our%20partners.%20At%20the%20UN%2C%20the%20India-UN%20Development%20Partnership%20Fund%2C%20a%20single%20country%20South-South%20initiative%2C%20has%20successfully%20developed%20a%20portfolio%20of%2075%20projects%20across%2056%20developing%20countries%20in%20just%206%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20along%20with%20United%20Nations%20General%20