ty%20surveillance%20footage%20emerged%20showing%20Boebert%20vaping%20as%20well%20as%20she%20and%20her%20date%20getting%20handsy%20with%20each%20other%20in%20their%20seats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'You%20are%20always%20under%20surveillance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDenver%20Arts%20%26amp%3B%20Venues%2C%20the%20city%20and%20county%20agency%20that%20operates%20the%20Buell%20Theater%2C%20would%20not%20comment%20to%20Insider%20on%20its%20security%20arrangements%20and%20cameras%2C%20but%20said%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20equipment%20is%20standard%20security%20protocol%20in%20many%20venues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWashington%20DC's%20Kennedy%20Center%2C%20for%20example%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20the%20nearly%202%2C500-seat%20venue%20%26quot%3Butilizes%20visible%20and%20unseen%20security%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20surveillance%20cameras%2C%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20the%20safety%20and%20security%20of%20our%20guests%2C%20artists%2C%20and%20staff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20famed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmom-rockettes-facial-recognition-kicked-out-2022-12%5C%22%3ERadio%20City%20Music%20Hall%20in%20New%20York%20City%20uses%20facial%20recognition%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%20among%20its%20various%20security%20measures%2C%20as%20Insider%20has%20previously%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20venue%20previously%20used%20that%20technology%20to%20deny%20a%20lawyer%20entry%20into%20a%20Rockettes%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMSG%20Entertainment%2C%20which%20owns%20the%206%2C000-seat%20venue%20as%20well%20as%20Madison%20Square%20Garden%20and%20the%20Chicago%20Theatre%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20its%20venues'%20security%20arrangements%20for%20this%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20is%20for%20certain%2C%20according%20to%20retired%20New%20York%20Police%20Department%20officer%20and%20safety%20and%20security%20expert%20Bill%20Stanton%20%E2%80%94%20the%20public%20is%20%26quot%3Balways%20being%20watched%26quot%3B%20by%20some%20type%20of%20surveillanc