22summary%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20on%20Saturday%20met%20the%20G20%20Independent%20Expert%20Group%20on%20strengthening%20of%20Multilateral%20Development%20Banks%20(MDBs).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fbanking%2Ffinance-minister-sitharaman-meets-g20-expert-group-on-strengthening-of-mdbs-123092300853_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20college%20sports%20teams%20unionize%3F%20We're%20about%20to%20find%20out.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Dartmouth%20basketball%20player%20dodges%20another%20player%20while%20in%20possession%20of%20the%20ball.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65048bce956dba001ace98a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPlayers%20on%20the%20Dartmouth%20men's%20NCAA%20basketball%20team%20have%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20unionize.%3Cp%3EDoug%20Austin%2FDartmouth%20Sports%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20Dartmouth%20men's%20basketball%20team%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20unionize%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ELike%20all%20student%20athletes%2C%20Dartmouth%20faces%20a%20number%20of%20barriers%20to%20unionization%20under%20federal%20labor%20law.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EA%20new%20labor%20case%20to%20be%20heard%20in%20November%2C%20however%2C%20could%20change%20everything.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDartmouth%20College%20is%20a%20Division%201%20school%20in%20the%20NCAA%2C%20competing%20in%20the%20Ivy%20League%20conference.%20They%20are%20known%20as%20the%20Big%20Green.%20And%20its%20men's%20basketball%20team%20just%20made%20a%20big%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fdartmouth-ncaa-mens-basketball-unionize-2023-9%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20with%20the%20National%20Labor%20Relations%20Board%2C%20or%20NLRB%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20asking%20to%20hold%20a%20union%20vote.%20This%20is%20a%20necessary%20step%20before%20they%20can%20hold%20an%20official%20vote%20to%20form%20a%20union%20that%20is%20sanctioned%20by%20the%20NLRB%2C%20an%20independent%20federal%20agency%20that%20protects%20workers'%20rights%20to%20organize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E'While%20we%20currently%20receive%20many%20forms%20of%20non-traditional%20compensation%2C%20these%20don't%20pay%20our%20bills%2C%20and%20so%20we%20are%20unionizing%20to%20be%20compensated%20like%20other%20student%20employees%2C%20with%20hourly%20wages%20similar%20to%20other%20student%20wages%20on%20campus%20or%20scholarships%2C%26quot%3B%20players%20Cade%20Haskins%20and%20Romeo%20Myrthil%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedartmouth.com%2Farticle%2F2023%2F09%2Fhaskins-and-myrthil-why-we-are-unionizing%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWhile%2520we%2520currently%2520receive%2520many%2Cwages%2520on%2520campus%2520or%2520scholarships.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopinion%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20The%20Dartmouth%2C%20the%20school's%20student-run%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20surprising%20and%20even%20exciting%20move%20for%20those%20following%20the%20business%20of%20college%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20comes%20just%20two%20years%20after%20the%20NCAA%20granted%20college%20athletes%20the%20right%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fncaa-college-athletes-who-could-make-millions-off-name-likeness-2021-7%3F_gl%3D1*lrkffj*_ga*MzE2MDMwODg2LjE2ODY1OTA0NDM.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5NDg4ODI1NC4yMDIuMC4xNjk0ODg5MTA5LjYwLjAuMA..%5C%22%3Emake%20money%20off%20their%20name%2C%20image%2C%20and%20likeness%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20And%20the%20ability%20to%20unionize%20would%20allow%20student%20athletes%20to%20collectively%20bargain%20for%20improved%20workplace%20conditions%20and%20even%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Michael%20LeRoy%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20labor%20and%20employment%20relations%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20at%20Urbana-Champaign%2C%20the%20bid%20is%20an%20important%20advancement%20for%20college%20athletes%20looking%20to%20achieve%20economic%20rights%20on%20par%20with%20professional%20athletes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20significant%20development%20because%2C%20conceptually%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20case%20for%20unionization%20beyond%20where%20it%20last%20stood%20before%20the%20National%20Labor%20Relations%20Board%2C%26quot%3B%20LeRoy%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20for%20unionizing%20college%20sports%20teams%20is%20a%20precarious%20one%2C%20as%20athletes%20face%20significant%20barriers%20under%20federal%20labor%20law.%20But%20that%20all%20could%20change%20as%20a%20judge%20gears%20up%20to%20argue%20a%20case%20this%20November%20that%20could%20eliminate%20those%20barriers%20and%20open%20the%20doors%20for%20college%20athletes%20to%20finally%20organize.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECollege%20athletes%20face%20barriers%20to%20unionization%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nlrb.gov%2Fguidance%2Fkey-reference-materials%2Fnational-labor-relations-act%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Labor%20Relations%20Act%20(NLRA)%3C%2Fa%3E%20poses%20two%20barriers%20that%20prevent%20college%20sports%20teams%20from%20unionizing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20the%20NLRA%20states%20you%20must%20be%20an%20employee%20to%20unionize.%20The%20NCAA%2C%20along%20with%20the%20colleges%20that%20house%20sports%20teams%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncaa.org%2Fsports%2F2021%2F5%2F11%2Four-division-i-priorities.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsider%20players%20amateurs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20not%20employees%20of%20their%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20NLRA%20does%20not%20protect%20public%20sector%20employees'%20right%20to%20unionize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECertainly%2C%20public%20sector%20employees%20can%20and%20do%20unionize%20%E2%80%94%20take%20public%20school%20teachers%2C%20for%20example%20%E2%80%94%20but%20their%20labor%20relations%20are%20governed%20by%20state%20statutes%20rather%20than%20the%20NLRA.%20That%20means%20that%20student%20athletes%20at%20public%20universities%2C%20even%20if%20they%20were%20considered%20employees%2C%20do%20not%20have%20their%20right%20to%20unionize%20protected%20by%20the%20NLRA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20did%20Dartmouth%20men's%20basketball%20file%20to%20unionize%2C%20then%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nlrb.gov%2Fcase%2F31-CA-290326%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENLRB%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20an%20administrative%20law%20judge%20will%20hear%20this%20November%20that%20could%20open%20the%20floodgates%20for%20college%20teams%20to%20unionize.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20College%20Players%20Association%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nonprofit%20advocating%20for%20NCAA%20reforms%20that%20bolster%20the%20rights%20of%20college%20athletes%20%E2%80%94%20brought%20the%20case%20against%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%2C%20Pac-12%2C%20and%20the%20NCAA%20in%20May.%20The%20nonprofit%20argued%20these%20organizations%20have%20violated%20USC%20athletes'%20rights%20under%20the%20NLRA%20by%20not%20considering%20them%20employees%2C%20according%20to%20the%20filed%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20case%20will%20be%20heard%20in%20November.%20A%20presiding%20administrative%20law%20judge%20will%20have%20to%20rule%20on%20whether%20USC%2C%20Pac-12%2C%20and%20the%20NCAA%20have%20indeed%20violated%20athletes'%20rights%20under%20the%20NLRA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20judge%20rules%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20National%20College%20Players%20Association%2C%20it%20would%20give%20both%20public%20and%20private%20college%20athletes%20the%20right%20to%20unionize%20under%20the%20NLRA%2C%20LeRoy%20said.%20Exactly%20what%20unionization%20would%20look%20like%2C%20though%2C%20is%20still%20unclear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20counsel%20of%20the%20NLRB%20is%20Jennifer%20Abruzzo%2C%20an%20outspoken%20advocate%20for%20college%20athlete%20unionization.%20Abruzzo%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nlrb.gov%2Fnews-outreach%2Fnews-story%2Fnlrb-general-counsel-jennifer-abruzzo-issues-memo-on-employee-status-of%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20supporting%20college%20athlete%20unionization%20and%20committed%20herself%20to%20pursuing%20the%20issue.%20Abruzzo%20argued%20college%20athletes%20are%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20employees%20because%20they%20%26quot%3Bperform%20services%20for%20institutions%20in%20return%20for%20compensation%20and%20subject%20to%20their%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20opinion%20piece%2C%20players%20Haskins%20and%20Myrthil%20said%20the%20team%20will%20fight%20to%20obtain%20employee%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOther%20than%20a%20set%20of%20rules%20that%20the%20schools%20impose%20on%20themselves%20through%20the%20Ivy%20League%20Agreement%2C%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20that%20basketball%20players%20shouldn't%20be%20considered%20student%20employees%20like%20students%20working%20any%20other%20campus%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Haskins%20and%20Myrthil%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHave%20other%20college%20sports%20teams%20tried%20to%20unionize%20before%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENorthwestern's%20football%20team%20filed%20a%20petition%20to%20unionize%20in%202014%20and%20got%20as%20far%20as%20holding%20a%20union%20vote.%20However%2C%20those%20ballots%20were%20never%20opened%20after%20a%20five-person%20NLRB%20panel%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nlrb.gov%2Fcase%2F13-RC-121359%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eruled%20against%20their%20bid%20in%202015%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20had%20two%20primary%20reasons%20for%20this%20ruling.%20First%2C%20there%20was%20the%20issue%20of%20employment%3A%20Athletes%20still%20were%20not%20considered%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20panel%20said%20Northwestern's%20unionization%20would%20be%20destabilizing%20because%20it%20would%20only%20affect%20one%20team%20in%20the%20league.%20For%20instance%2C%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20Northwestern%20went%20on%20strike%20but%20the%20rest%20of%20their%20league%20couldn't%2C%20especially%20public%20schools%20in%20the%20same%20league%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20unworkable%20to%20have%20one%20school%20bargaining%20for%20pay%20and%20benefits%20and%20so%20forth%20when%20the%20other%20schools%20can't%2C%26quot%3B%20LeRoy%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20Northwestern%20went%20out%20on%20strike%20and%20the%20rest%20could%20not%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20given%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-workers-strikes-reach-a-record-high-since-2000-2023-9%5C%22%3Eshifting%20labor%20landscape%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Aburzzo's%20dedication%20to%20college%20athlete%20unionization%2C%20it's%20possible%20Northwestern's%20ruling%20may%20not%20hold%20up%2C%20LeRoy%20said.%20A%20decision%20in%20favor%20of%20the%20National%20College%20Players%20Association%20in%20the%20USC%20case%20would%20overturn%20the%20Northwestern%20decision.%20It%20would%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20discussions%20about%20the%20best%20way%20forward%2C%20allowing%20the%20NLRB%20to%20explore%20questions%20in%20the%20coming%20years%20about%20if%20and%20how%20teams%20could%20unionize%20across%20leagues%20and%20divisions%2C%20according%20to%20LeRoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20those%20questions%20will%20be%20the%20repercussions%20that%20come%20with%20considering%20student%20athletes%20employees.%20It's%20possible%20not%20all%20college%20athletes%20will%20be%20in%20favor%20of%20such%20a%20thing%2C%20said%20Irwin%20Kishner%2C%20cochair%20of%20the%20Sports%20Law%20Group%20at%20Herrick%20Feinstein%2C%20a%20New%20York%20law%20firm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKishner%20said%20the%20label%20could%20give%20coaches%20the%20ability%20to%20fire%20at%20will%20or%20cause%20universities%20to%20cut%20low-profit%20teams%20because%20of%20increased%20expenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20litany%20of%20things%20that%20come%20from%20being%20an%20employee%20and%20there's%20a%20litany%20of%20things%20that%20come%20from%20not%20being%20an%20employee%2C%26quot%3B%20Kishner%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BTo%20get%20them%20all%20down%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20at%20this%20juncture%20to%20predict%20where%20all%20this%20lands%20would%20be%20very%20difficult.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20when%20we'll%20get%20final%20answers%2C%20Kishner%20and%20LeRoy%20both%20agreed%3A%20It%20could%20be%20years%20before%20we%20know%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20union%20bid%20by%20the%20Dartmouth%20men's%20basketball%20players.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-college-sports-teams-student-athletes-form-union-dartmouth-basketball-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695482581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F650df1c0e453d50019f7e871%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-college-sports-teams-student-athletes-form-union-dartmouth-basketball-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Some%20college%20athletes%2C%20like%20the%20Dartmouth%20men's%20basketball%20team%2C%20want%20to%20form%20a%20union.%20An%20upcoming%20case%20will%20decide%20if%20they%20can.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Hawkinson%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-college-sports-teams-student-athletes-form-union-dartmouth-basketball-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl