ncy%2C%20any%20leave%20that%20a%20faculty%20member%20is%20eligible%20for%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20granted%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20routine%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20restrictions%20have%20been%20imposed%20on%20such%20leaves%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJNU%20professor%20Surjit%20Mujumdar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20asking%20for%20a%20leave%20amounts%20to%20harassment.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20process%20of%20granting%20leave%2C%20the%20process%20of%20promotions%2C%20or%20any%20such%20case%2C%20any%20matter%20that%20teachers%20have%20to%20take%20up%2C%20they%20are%20subjected%20to%20all%20kinds%20of%20harassment%20and%20victimization.%20No%20one%20knows%20where%20the%20file%20is%2C%20where%20the%20application%20is%20going.%20People%20have%20to%20run%20up%20and%20down%20the%20administrative%20offices%20and%20spend%20long%20periods%20of%20time%20in%20that%20particular%20process.%20The%20administration%20has%20built%20this%20kind%20of%20insensitivity%2C%20where%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20accountability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETeachers%20attribute%20the%20reasons%20for%20such%20an%20appalling%20condition%20to%20bureaucratization%20and%20administrative%20apathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F673102717%2FJNU-State-of-the-University-Report%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20JNU%20State%20of%20the%20University%20Report%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EJNU%20State%20of%20the%20University%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F524756983%2FTaniya-Roy%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Taniya%20Roy's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3ETaniya%20Roy%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F673102717%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-X1fNYrG6Sbi0Zsik