ccounts%20for%2040%25%20of%20the%20global%20rice%20trade.%20The%20export%20ban%20by%20India%2C%20therefore%2C%20has%20come%20to%20affect%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20for%20whom%20rice%20is%20the%20staple%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRice%2C%20especially%20in%20Africa%2C%20can%20certainly%20bring%20potential%20conflict%20or%20social%20unrest%2C%20which%20at%20this%20moment%20in%20time%20would%20be%20quite%20dangerous%2C%E2%80%9D%20told%20Lario%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-rice-export-ban-is-fueling-risk-of-social-unrest-un-says-11413561.html%5C%22%3Einterview%20to%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CExport%20bans%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20impact%2C%20especially%20on%20the%20most%20vulnerable%2C%20by%20raising%20prices%20and%20having%20a%20shock%20on%20prices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CGenerally%20they%20are%20not%20positive%2C%20neither%20for%20the%20local%20populations%20in%20the%20medium%20term%2C%20nor%20for%20the%20other%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20lamented%20that%20some%20regions%20in%20Africa%20that%20are%20more%20dependent%20on%20rice%20imports%20are%20already%20witnessing%20adverse%20impacts%20due%20to%20higher%20prices.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20understand%20that%20many%20of%20these%20people%20who%20consume%20this%20type%20of%20crop%20are%20sometimes%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20poverty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20saying%20that%20the%20impacts%20of%20bans%20%E2%80%9Cgo%20beyond%20the%20borders%20of%20the%20countries%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20added%20that%20rice%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20concern%E2%80%9D%20for%20security%2C%20much%20more%20than%20wheat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2020%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Directorate%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20issued%20a%20notification%2C%20banning%20exports%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20%E2%80%9Cwith%20immediate%20effect%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20order%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20availability%20of%20non-basmati%20white%20rice%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20and%20to%20allay%20the%20rise%20in%20prices%20in%20the%20domestic%20market%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20amended%20the%20Export%20Policy%20of%20the%20above%20variety%20from%20%E2%80%98Free%20with%20export%20duty%20of%2020%25%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98Prohibited%E2%80%99%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20notification%20had%20said.%20%E2%80%9CDomestic%20prices%20of%20rice%20are%20on%20an%20increasing%20trend.%20Retail%20prices%20have%20increased%20by%2011.5%25%20over%20a%20year%20and%203%25%20over%20the%20past%20month.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20decision%20came%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Russia%20stating%20that%20it%20would%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20Black%20Seas%20Grain%20Initiative%2C%20resulting%20in%20huge%20anxiety%20in%20the%20global%20market%20and%20consequent%20rise%20in%20food%20prices%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20export%20ban%20by%20India%20is%20reminiscent%20of%202008%20when%20the%20world%20witnessed%20a%20global%20rice%20crisis%2C%20putting%20the%20lives%20of%20100%20million%20people%20at%20risk.%20Mostly%2C%20populations%20living%20in%20sub-Saharan%20Africa%20were%20the%20worst%20affected.%20The%20crisis%20was%20spawned%20by%20the%20decision%20of%20India%20and%20Vietnam%20to%20restrict%20their%20rice%20exports.%20Food%20shortages%20and%20surging%20prices%20had%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20political%20unrest%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20leading%20to%20the%20Arab%20Spring%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20dislodging%20of%20several%20governments%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695470182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F19161235%2F31764443254_73b92a3ef0_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Frisk-of-social-unrest-in-asia-africa-due-to-indias-rice-export-