reatment-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigital%20age%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20various%20wearable%20tracking%20devices%20available%2C%2064%2C851%20people%20go%20missing%20every%20month%20in%20India%2C%20according%20to%20the%20World%20Population%20Review%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20if%20there%20was%20a%20way%20in%20which%20we%20as%20citizens%20could%20do%20more%20than%20just%20sympathise%20for%20the%20missing%20people%20or%20their%20families%3F%20Moved%20by%20these%20reports%2C%20a%20young%20student%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAkshay%20Ridlan%2C%20who%20was%20a%20UPSC%20aspirant%20in%202019%2C%20would%20read%20the%20newspapers%20every%20morning%20as%20part%20of%20his%20preparation%20for%20the%20exam.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20would%20come%20across%20these%20reports.%20He%20was%20only%2020%20years%20old%20then.%20This%20shook%20something%20in%20the%20youngster%20and%20left%20him%20deeply%20disturbed%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chat%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Akshay%20talks%20about%20his%20motivation%20to%20do%20something%20about%20this%20grim%20reality.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20stories%20of%20the%20missing%20children%20haunted%20me%2C%20particularly%20of%20an%20autistic%20kid%2C%20Tarun%20Gupta%2C%20who%20went%20missing%20on%201%20October%2C%202019.%20The%2017-year-old%20was%20made%20to%20board%20a%20train%20by%20an%20RPF%20officer%2C%20instead%20of%20getting%20him%20help.%20I%20felt%20devastated%20for%20that%20child%20and%20his%20parents.%20I%20felt%20like%20this%20problem%20has%20to%20be%20addressed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%3Cstrong%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20who%20lose%20their%20way%20or%20forget%20their%20identity%20are%20usually%20suffering%20from%20illnesses%20like%20dementia%2C%20age-related%20incapacities%2C%20or%20other%20mental%20disabilities.%20Young%20children%20with%20disabilities%2C%20and%20ones%20on%20the%20autism%20spectrum%20are%20especially%20at%20risk%20in%20these%20scenarios.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20now%2024-year-old%20IT%20professional%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20tech-based%20solution%20to%20effectively%20end%20this%20problem.%20Akshay%20launched%20Project%20Chetna%20on%2012%20September%202023%2C%20and%20through%20it%2C%20he%20came%20up%20with%20unique%20QR%20tags%2C%20which%20can%20be%20worn%20around%20the%20neck%20inside%20a%20pendant.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20QR%20codes%2C%20when%20scanned%2C%20would%20provide%20the%20contact%20details%20and%20medical%20information%20about%20the%20person%20who%20wears%20it.%20These%20tags%20are%20aimed%20to%20help%20vulnerable%20patients%20and%20citizens%20with%20mental%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20moments%20of%20disorientation%20or%20when%20people%20are%20lost%2C%20this%20QR%20tag%20can%20provide%20essential%20details%2C%20such%20as%20their%20medical%20condition%2C%20emergency%20contacts%2C%20and%20home%20address%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Akshay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20the%20lost%20find%20their%20way%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxQsH9BpAN4%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxQsH9BpAN4%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3