gement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tripura%20IAS%20Officer%E2%80%99s%20Idea%20Is%20Preventing%20Girls%20From%20Leaving%20School%3B%20Stopped%2090%20Child%20Marriages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20on%20her%20way%20home%20from%20school%2C%2016-year-old%20Jyotsana%20Akhtar%20from%20Tripura%E2%80%99s%20Amzadnagar%20village%20heard%20people%20whispering%20while%20looking%20at%20her.%20When%20she%20overheard%20their%20conversation%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20aback%20to%20learn%20that%20her%20marriage%20was%20fixed!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20returned%20home%2C%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Emaa%3C%2Fem%3E%20didn%E2%80%99t%20mention%20anything%20about%20the%20marriage.%20I%20found%20out%20from%20the%20villagers%20that%20I%20was%20to%20marry%20a%20man%20twice%20my%20age%20who%20had%20been%20divorced.%20It%20seemed%20like%20all%20my%20fears%20were%20soon%20to%20turn%20into%20reality%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20if%20I%20would%20ever%20return%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jyotsana%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20retaliated%20and%20refused%20to%20get%20married%20so%20early.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20study%20further%20and%20get%20a%20good%20job%2C%20if%20possible%20earn%20better%20than%20the%20man%20with%20whom%20my%20marriage%20was%20fixed.%20But%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20understand%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20week%2C%20she%20approached%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20school%20club%2C%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20teachers%20with%20her%20problem.%20Through%20them%2C%20the%20district%20administration%20intervened%20and%20prevented%20her%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A