%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20more%20about%20the%20initiative%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20battle%20against%20child%20marriages%20in%20Tripura%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBeti%20Bachao%2C%20Beti%20Padhao%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20was%20started%20in%202020%20by%20the%20then%20collector%20Debapriya%20Bardhan%20to%20educate%20girls%20on%20adolescence%20and%20reproductive%20health.%20But%20the%20initiative%20turned%20dormant%20as%20schools%20shut%20amid%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F257746%2Fias-hero-karnataka-ceo-zilla-parishad-prevents-child-marriage%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Saju%20Vaheed%20%E2%80%94%20a%202015%20batch%20IAS%20officer%20from%20Kerala%20%E2%80%94%20took%20over%20and%20joined%20as%20the%20Collector%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20and%20revived%20the%20initiative%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Saju%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20reviving%20this%20project%2C%20I%20got%20to%20know%20that%20many%20female%20students%20of%20Classes%208%2C%209%2C%20and%2010%20were%20dropping%20out%20of%20school.%20The%20education%20department%20informed%20me%20that%20it%20was%20because%20of%20child%20marriages.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20South%20Tripura%20district%20%E2%80%94%20Saju%20Vaheed.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1695216993-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330395%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%2090%20young%20girls%20have%20been%20saved%20from%20early%20marriages%2C%20thanks%20to%20IAS%20officer%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20in%20mid-2022%2C%20we%20conducted%20a%20survey%20and%20found%20out%20that%20215%20such%20girls%20got%20married%20in%202020%20and%20the%20number%20was%20209%20in%202021.%20This%20comprised%20over%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20dropout%20rate%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20that%20they%20observed%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20girls%20were%20getting%20married%20when%20they%20were%20between%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20means%20that%20girls%20were%20getting%20married%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20were%20entering%20puberty%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3ENational%20Family%20Health%20Survey-5%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years%20in%20Tripura%20%E2%80%94%20the%20third%20highest%20after%20West%20Bengal%20(41.6%20percent)%20and%20Bihar%20(40.8%20percent).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20a%20high%20percentage%20of%20underage%20girls%20are%20getting%20married%20in%20Tripura.%20Another%20issue%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20detect%20ongoing%20child%20marriages%20because%20they%20often%20involve%20local%20cooperation.%20Typically%2C%20we%20only%20find%20out%20about%20the%20marriage%20through%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20boyfriend%2C%20and%20sometimes%20we%E2%80%99re%20notified%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20making%20it%20very%20difficult%20to%20prevent%20the%20marriage%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20departments%20like%20health%20and%20social%20welfare%20would%20only%20get%20to%20know%20about%20these%20marriages%20when%20these%20young%20girls%20got%20pregnant%20and%20reached%20out%20to%20avail%20government%20schemes.%20Even%20though%20the%20departments%20knew%20it%20was%20illegal%20for%20these%20young%20girls%20to%20be%20married%2C%20they%20found%20themselves%20helpless%20when%20they%20found%20out%20about%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20early%20pregnancies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saju%20Vaheed%20brought%20together%20all%20the%20departments%20to%20utilise%20Balika%20Manch%20for%20child%20marriage%20prevention.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-2-1695217326-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.theb