0to%20school%20citing%20legal%20complications%20of%20the%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20formed%20WhatsApp%20groups%20of%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%2C%20women%20school%20management%20committees%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Childline%2C%20child%20welfare%20committees%2C%20and%20district-level%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20WhatsApp%20group%2C%20%3Cem%3EBalika%20Manch%3C%2Fem%3E%20representatives%20inform%20the%20group%20members%20about%20the%20case.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20cases%20where%20the%20parents%20are%20not%20convinced%2C%20then%20administrative%20support%20is%20sought.%20This%20is%20when%20our%20second%20layer%20of%20officials%20comes%20into%20the%20picture.%20It%20comprises%20a%20one-stop%20centre%20(where%20young%20girls%20can%20reach%20out%20to%20experts%20for%20counselling)%2C%20a%20district%20child%20protection%20unit%2C%20counsellors%2C%20psychologists%2C%20and%20legal%20practitioners%20who%20reach%20out%20to%20families%20to%20convince%20them.%20Most%20of%20the%20cases%20get%20resolved%20in%20the%20second%20layer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20were%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-3-1695217359-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330400%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%20Tripura%2C%2040.1%20percent%20of%20women%20aged%2020%E2%80%9324%20years%20are%20married%20before%20the%20age%20of%2018%20years.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20the%20families%20start%20questioning%20our%20rights%20to%20prevent%20the%20marriage%2C%20we%20activate%20our%20third%20layer.%20My%20sub-divisional%20magistrate%20rushes%20to%20the%20spot%20and%20tells%20the%20parents%20that%20the%20administration%20shall%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family%20as%20child%20marriage%20is%20a%20punishable%20offence.%20But%20even%20then%2C%20if%20families%20go%20ahead%2C%20we%20send%20police%20officers%20to%20their%20homes%20and%20register%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20family.%20We%20then%20get%20an%20affidavit%20signed%20by%20the%20parents%20stating%20that%20they%E2%80%99ll%20not%20marry%20off%20their%20daughters%20until%20they%20are%2018%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20collector.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20timely%20intervention%2C%20Saju%20has%20been%20able%20to%20prevent%2090%20planned%20child%20marriages%20in%20the%20district%20in%20the%20past%20year%20with%20the%20help%20of%20158%20school%20clubs%20across%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20if%20we%20are%20able%20to%20continue%20this%20way%20for%20another%20year%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20eradicate%20child%20marriages%20in%20our%20district.%20Seeing%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20work%2C%20the%20state%20government%20aims%20to%20expand%20this%20initiative%20across%20Tripura.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20work%20is%20deeply%20satisfying%20to%20me%20because%20when%20these%20girls%20talk%20to%20me%2C%20I%20realise%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20preventing%20marriages%3B%20we%E2%80%99re%20saving%20lives.%20These%20young%20girls%20now%20have%20a%20platform%20to%20voice%20their%20concerns.%20While%20I%E2%80%99m%20involved%20in%20various%20other%20development%20projects%2C%20this%20one%20is%20particularly%20dear%20to%20me.%20I%20believe%20it%20will%20ensure%20a%20better%20future%20for%20generations%20to%20come%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saju.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Saju%20Vaheed.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695218864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FSouth-Tripura-1-1695217206.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D330387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tripura%20is%20notorious%20for%20child%20marriages%20with%20four%20in%2010%20girls%20getting%20married%20before%20turning%2018.%20In%20a%20novel%20approach%2C%20South%20Tripura%20District%20Magistrate%20Saju%20Vaheed%20revived%20%E2%80%98Balika%20Manch%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20school%20club%20cum%20platform%20to%20prevent%20young%20girls%20from%20dropping%20out%20of%20school%20and%20getting%20married.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330387%2Fias-officer-district-magistrate-saju-vaheed-balika-manch-prevent-child-marriage-south-tripura%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Startup%20Will%20Help%20You%20Find%20Less%20Crowded%20Fuel%20Stations%2C%20For%20CNG%20%26amp%3B%20EVs%20Too%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20got%20his%20licence%20at%2018%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20tried%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306067%2Fcollege-dropout-launches-ev-startup-builds-made-in-india-luxury-electric-suv-pravaig%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriving%20a%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20every%20other%20person.%20However%2C%20he%20would%20often%20end%20up%20getting%20into%20accidents%2C%20and%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20other%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20stop%20driving.%20This%20made%20him%20a%20regular%20user%20of%20cab%20services%20like%20Ola%20and%20Uber.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20decision%20to%20stay%20off%20the%20roads%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20startup%20idea%20which%20aimed%20to%20decongest%20fuel%20stations%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Vaibhav%2C%20an%20engineer%20from%20BITS%20Pilani%2C%20was%20doing%20an%20internship%20in%20Greater%20Noida.%20During%20the%20half-hour%20commute%20between%20his%20home%20and%20office%2C%20he%20used%20to%20strike%20up%20conversations%20with%20cab%20drivers.%20They%20mainly%20drove%20CNG%20vehicles%20and%20this%20is%20where%20he%20learnt%20about%20their%20biggest%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20drivers%20complained%20of%20one%20single%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20the%20line%20at%20the%20fuel%20station%20was%20very%20long.%20Out%20of%20the%2010%20hours%20they%20spent%20on%20the%20road%2C%20an%20hour%20was%20wasted%20at%20these%20fuel%20stations%20daily.%20The%20cab%20drivers%20told%20me%20that%20they%20lost%2010%20percent%20of%20their%20daily%20earnings%20idling%20away%20in%20the%20queue%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaibhav%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%20be%20wonderful%20if%20the%20cab%20driver%20could%20know%20which%20fuel%20station%20had%20a%20lesser%20waiting%20time%3F%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20%E2%80%98Nawgati%E2%80%99%20came%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%2020%20then%2C%20and%20in%20his%20third-year%20of%20engineering%2C%20Vaibhav%20thought%20that%20this%20problem%20must%20have%20been%20solved%20by%20someone.%20To%20his%20surprise%2C%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20solution%2C%20he%20started%20working%20on%20one%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20Aalaap%20Nair%20and%20Aryan%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20researched%20various%20pain%20points%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%20customers%20and%20fuel%20stations.%20They%20then%20spoke%20to%20fuel%20providers%20and%20examined%20their%20in-house%20challenges%20and%20difficulties.%20After%20this%2C%20they%20built%20the%20technology%2C%20a%20queue%20management%20platform%2C%20which%20would%20help%20both%20fuel%20stations%20and%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20fuel%20companies%20improve%20efficiency%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nawgati%20founders%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-founders2-1695131172-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330322%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENawgati%20founders%20%E2%80%93%20Aryan%20Sisodia%2C%20Vaibhav%20Kaushik%20and%20Aalaap%20Nair.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20came%20up%20with%20two%20solutions%2C%20an%20app%20for