2C%20which%20helps%20fuel%20pumps%20manage%20congestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Nawgati%20helps%20consumers%2C%20especially%20cab%20drivers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nawgati%20app%20helps%20consumers%20find%20nearest%20fuel%20stations%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-170x300.jpg%20170w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-500x883.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-768x1356.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-870x1536.jpg%20870w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fnawgati-app-min-1695131402-150x265.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330324%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221907%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Nawgati%20app%20helps%20consumers%20find%20the%20nearest%20fuel%20stations.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20solution%20was%20built%20with%20cab%20drivers%20in%20mind%2C%20to%20help%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304454%2Ftwo-friends-climate-tech-startup-climes-helps-neutralise-carbon-footprint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esave%20time%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20this%2C%20the%20company%20has%20developed%20an%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNawgati%20fueling%20app%20