%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20hail%20from%20the%20same%20village%20as%20the%20index%20case%2C%20the%20doctors%20were%20alert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20would%20a%20healthy%2C%20young%20adult%20die%20of%20pneumonia%20in%20just%20three%20days%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20unusual%20in%20the%20case%20of%20normal%20bronchopneumonia.%20We%20started%20probing%20in%20detail.%20We%20followed%20the%20Nipah%20protocols%20in%20handling%20the%20body%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20it%20to%20the%20family.%C2%A0We%20sent%20his%20sample%20also%20to%20NIV%20the%20same%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20that%20there%20was%20an%20overlap%20between%20this%20patient%20and%20the%20first%20patient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20relative%20who%20was%20being%20treated%20in%20the%20same%20hospital%20as%20the%20index%20case.%20We%20got%20the%20discharge%20summary%20of%20that%20patient%20to%20establish%20the%20exact%20connection.%20He%20had%20been%20in%20the%20same%20ICU%20as%20the%20first%20patient%20who%20died%20on%2029%20August%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20critical%20care%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%2042-year-old%20man%20and%20two%20of%20the%20four%20admitted%20tested%20positive%20for%20Nipah%20virus.%20Three%20others%20have%20also%20tested%20positive%20in%20Kozhikode%2C%20taking%20the%20total%20Nipah%20cases%20currently%20to%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20Dr%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20team%20has%20helped%20the%20state%20government%20establish%20containment%20zones%20and%20trace%20all%20contacts%20of%20these%20patients%20and%20isolate%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%202018%20experience%20helped%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FF6ERlubaYAA9NDF-1694787971.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C