0to%20help%20cool%20the%20wind%20that%20enters%20her%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20house%20more%20sustainable%2C%20Anupa%20also%20added%20water%20gutters%20on%20the%20roof%20to%20use%20the%20rainwater.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20from%20the%20gutters%20flows%20into%20the%20two%20ponds%20that%20we%20have%2C%20and%20we%20also%20store%20it%20to%20use%20the%20water%20for%20landscaping%20the%20house.%20Although%20my%20parents%20did%20not%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20the%20gutters%2C%20I%20wanted%20the%20house%20to%20be%20as%20sustainable%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anupa%20was%20able%20to%20renovate%20the%20house%20fully%20for%20just%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fveedu-1-3-1694786857-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330104%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAnupa%20was%20able%20to%20renovate%20the%20house%20fully%20for%20Rs%2030%20lakh.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Anupa%20Kurian%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20encountering%20some%20opposition%20due%20to%20its%20divergence%20from%20current%20trends%2C%20she%20has%20chosen%20to%20preserve%20the%20original%20