l%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20few%20tribal%20hamlets%20in%20this%20village.%20The%20occupation%20of%20the%20residents%20is%20to%20collect%20raw%20materials%20from%20the%20forest.%20There%20are%20no%20transport%20facilities%20to%20these%20hamlets%20as%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20a%20%3Cem%3Epucca%3C%2Fem%3E%20road.%20When%20I%20joined%2C%20my%20first%20mission%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20these%20children%20come%20to%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Archana%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArchana%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20get%20those%20children%20to%20school.%20She%20started%20visiting%20those%20tribal%20hamlets%20and%20spoke%20to%20the%20parents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20proper%20houses%20or%20even%20clothes%20to%20wear.%20They%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20school%20as%20no%20one%20from%20there%20was%20enrolled.%20I%20visited%20them%20daily%20for%2015%20days%20to%20convince%20them.%20I%20told%20them%20how%20essential%20education%20is%20and%20how%20it%20can%20help%20their%20children%20lead%20a%20better%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Archana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20exalted%20the%20benefits%20of%20education%20and%20the%20change%20it%20enables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20show%20them%20videos%20of%20people%20who%20came%20from%20similar%20backgrounds%20and%20are%20in%20a%20good%20position%20today.%20Through%20education%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20transform%20their%20lives.%20I%20urged%20these%20parents%20to%20give%20their%20children%20the%20same%20opportunity%20to%20progress%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMany%20Problems%20Laced%20The%20Journey%20to%20Success%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Farchana-16